------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party components
------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Prism CLI and library have NO third-party runtime dependencies. They
use only the Python 3.12+ standard library.

The optional registry Worker (templates/registry/worker/), used only by
teams who self-host a skills registry, has the following development
dependencies (not distributed, build/deploy only). All are permissively
licensed:

  - wrangler ............... MIT License ......... https://github.com/cloudflare/workers-sdk
  - @cloudflare/workers-types  MIT/Apache-2.0 .... https://github.com/cloudflare/workerd
  - typescript ............. Apache-2.0 .......... https://github.com/microsoft/TypeScript

AI extraction is performed by invoking the user's locally installed and
authenticated IDE CLIs (`claude` or Cursor `agent`). These tools are NOT
bundled or redistributed by Prism.

